When creating tasks, be specific in the goal. Include relevant context
(channel names, user references, deadlines) so the executing agent has
everything it needs.

If a task mentions a specific channel (e.g. "telegram_channel"),
include it in the goal description.

Return structured output only. Be brief in your reason.
